Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:02.93,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:04.12,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Kozu.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…There’s… something I have to tell you…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:14.25,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…What?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:19.54,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It’s not like I don’t have anything to say to you, but…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.65,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I haven’t changed my mind from earlier.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:24.25,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,No matter–\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I know.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:29.42,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You were completely right.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:32.72,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Then…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:34.38,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:39.26,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Are you going… to that other school?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:46.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I was mistaken.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:53.35,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What was most important to me was becoming a praiseworthy school idol,\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:59.57,Kozue,,0,0,0,,winning Love Live!, and protecting the legacy of the Hasunosora School Idol Club.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:03.37,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s why I intended to reject the scouting offer…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:07.03,Kozue,,0,0,0,,and why I decided to change our choreography.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.25,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You said that earlier.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:12.43,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I know.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.16,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s why I said I was mistaken.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:18.98,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I was wrong.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:22.76,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I know that now.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:24.77,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Kozu.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:27.34,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.44,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri, I…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:35.72,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I didn’t want to be separated from you.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:37.09,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Huh?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:42.08,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’ve had such an enjoyable experience in this club.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:46.53,Kozue,,0,0,0,,We had seniors I looked up to and delightful friends to be with.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:51.28,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Even if we came to lose some of those…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:56.96,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Of all that I aspired to be when we first met, you’re all that’s left.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:58.17,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:01.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m no longer pretending to be strong.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:09.22,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I never even realized how I truly felt.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:10.93,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Kozu…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.79,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But… you’re…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:17.91,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with being scouted.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.44,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Please forget those excuses I gave earlier…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:23.72,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And listen to how I truly feel.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:28.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I just… don’t want to leave you all.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.18,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And back then…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:34.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I didn’t want you to leave me.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:37.95,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s why I don’t want to go anywhere.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:43.64,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…My dream is no longer just my own.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:47.83,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s a dream we want to fulfill together.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.45,Kozue,,0,0,0,,So…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I want to make that dream come true, right here!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:54.34,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Is that…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.43,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,How you really…?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:04.71,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry I haven’t said any of this before now.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.93,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…The words I wanted to say, and the words I should have said all along…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.16,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Until just now, I never realized what they were.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,So… what do you say?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:24.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m sure that I’m no longer lying to myself…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.68,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Or at least, I think so.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:32.38,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:37.09,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I finally hear your true feelings.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:43.90,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I’m happy that you do.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.17,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kozu…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:51.49,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to apologize for.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:52.85,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,No…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:04:00.53,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,All I knew was that you were hiding something from me at the qualifiers.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.81,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I should have asked.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:09.19,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I had…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.49,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Maybe.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.39,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I should have told you.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Even though my reason was selfish.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.33,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpaaaai!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri-senpai!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.44,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my… if it isn’t the knot that ties us together.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.11,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Ties us…?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:33.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’d rather you didn’t cut it off there…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:36.31,Kozue,,0,0,0,,We’re over here, you two!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.28,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Apologies for the wait.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:45.40,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But thanks to you two, everything’s okay now!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:49.73,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Wait… you still can’t trust my “okay”s, huh…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:54.41,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I… how do I say this…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:58.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ahaha, don’t worry, we get it, Kozue-senpai!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:04.29,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You’re saying that things are all okay between you two now, right?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.85,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m really happy to see it.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:14.91,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I… couldn’t find Tsuzuri-senpai, so I was getting really worried.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:16.91,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But I feel better now.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:20.54,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:24.31,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry for worrying you two.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m very grateful for your help.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.46,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ehehe…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Of course.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:37.10,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But now I’m sure we can have the best performance ever.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:38.87,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I agree.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:43.42,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I feel I can perform that song perfectly now.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:49.46,Kozue,,0,0,0,,After all… our feelings are now all as one.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:50.97,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Alright!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.98,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Looks like everything’s coming together perfectly!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.51,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai, lead us back into it!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.89,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Me?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:04.81,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I think it would be quite awkward if I led you all at this moment…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.85,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Just do things as you normally would.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.17,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.57,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I believe in you.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.57,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Alright, fine.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.20,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Then…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:22.25,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, let’s do our best to practice for the Nadeshiko Festival!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:28.58,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That way, we can show everyone watching the festival a performance worthy of the School Idol Club–\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.58,Kozue,,0,0,0,,No…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:34.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Because I want to have the best performance, together with all of you!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
